<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich von Seckendorff zu Altheim</head><p>Der Rat teilt wegen des Streits mit N. Feldbrecher mit, dass sich Peter Lutz, Bürger zu Nürnberg, sich zunächst versöhnlich mit ihm ausgesprochen hat und ihn sichert.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_228" id="113v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l1"><expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Secke<ex>n</ex>dorff</expan> cʒü Altheim / . </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_228_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Lucʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_line_1576590235008_4777"><expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir Jn beſant vnd cʒe rede geſacʒt / vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hat vns ge </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l7"><expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / . Er hab mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> veltprecher in gelimppf 
<add><ab facs="#facs_228_line_1576590238271_4782">geredt </ab></add> / vvie Jm ein be </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l8">ſcheıdenheit noch 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew </del> awſſtünd / vnd alſo ſprech <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>veltprech<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l9">Er ſolt es an Jn <expan>ſecʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> / . Da ſprech er / Er wolt es <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> tün / . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l10">vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſülle </del> ſprıcht auch nemlıch / daʒ Jr vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>hellff<ex>er</ex></expan> vor Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l11"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> ſıcher ſein ſüllet <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lich</expan> / vnd vvo wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l12"><expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb vnd <expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l13">wir allcʒit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> Sexta <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Valentinj / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_228" id="113v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Secke<ex>n</ex>dorff</expan> czü Altheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Lucze<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir in besant und cze rede gesaczt und
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hat uns
                            ge<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, er hab mit
                            <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Veltprecher in gelimppf <add>geredt</add>,
                        wie im ein bescheidenheit noch awsstünd; und also sprech
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Veltprech<ex>er</ex></expan>, er solt es an in
                            <expan>secze<ex>n</ex></expan>. Da sprech er, er wolt es
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> tün. Und spricht auch nemlich, daz ir
                        und <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hellff<ex>er</ex></expan> vor im <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> sache <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> sicher sein
                        süllet <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan>. Und wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb und
                            <expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        allczit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> sexta <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
                        Valentini.</ab>
</div>
